---
title: Korean-Style Crispy Chicken with Charred Corn Slaw & Sriracha Mayo
description: Our eyes are wide open with anticipation for crispy and richly sauced chicken, it’s simply irresistible. In a bowl of charred corn slaw with ponzu sauce that will make your jaw drop and don’t get us started on the sriracha mayo. In fact, let’s dive right in and enjoy!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
